dmca.title: copyright infringement
dmca.body:
To Whom It May Concern:

 

The URL in question is currently not accessible as of 5:02:22 p.m.
(GMT-6) on January 17, 2007 because it requires proprietary log-in
information to access it.

 

Legal Response Team

The Planet


________________________________

From: junevois625@aol.com [mailto:junevois625@aol.com] 
Sent: Monday, January 15, 2007 3:38 PM
To: Copyright
Subject: copyright infringement


A post I made on a copyrighted website forum was copied and pasted onto
another website forum without my permission.  I asked that the post be
removed and was told it would not be. 
 
The website forum is www.whalingcity.info and the link to the post is:
 
http://www.whalingcity.info/THEFORUM/viewtopic.php?t=501
 
 
The email address of the person responsible for posting this is:
Redsoxgirl1968@yahoo.com
 
I declare, under penalty of perjury, that the statements I have made
about this infringement are true to the best of my ability.
 
If you need more information, please contact me.
 
June Voisine
